description: For upcoming american elections, it is helpful to provide citizens (us residents or not) details about american elections processes. This skill  enables to provide definition and/or  details about some general items or political terms   like : ballot initiative, battleground state, bellwether state, bill of rights, blue state, bundler, capitol,caucus, constitution, delegates, electoral College, federal election commission, founding fathers, front loading, grand old party, swing states, primary, caucus, donkey, elephant, inauguration, independent, lobbyist, oval office, public funding, purple state, red state, second amendment, super tuesday, tea party, third party candidate, wedge issue, wonk, ....
name: American Elections
